{"tid":1995152,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【我屌晒你哋老母！】51行動文宣片打台灣戰線你知唔知？","createTime":"2020-04-30T04:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T07:19:33.000Z","uid":231886,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9204a4066d1a1efb61a5a1982f893ffac4fcbe","tid":1995152,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T04:42:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係屌晒你哋老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n#大家快啲入去幫推 #CLS<br />\n#Comment #Like #Subscribe<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">除罩，有香港獨立，有前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲回應緊台灣條大聲說話<br />\n推佢老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108411783950390/posts/173460727445495/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108411783950390%2Fposts%2F173460727445495%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2F2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=1f55aa67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108411783950390/posts/173460727445495/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nYouTube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TDksm1_42wU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTDksm1_42wU&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2F2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=1ba4c429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TDksm1_42wU</a><br />\n<br />\n============================<br />\n【香港人，請記著，我哋無繼續低沉嘅本錢！】<br />\n<br />\n今次，係我地抗拒赤化嘅最後一次機會！<br />\n<br />\n抗爭將近一週年，30多個真&middot;香港人工會，聯同Project R，要藉此機會向世界疾呼，抗爭仍未結束，革命不應被淡忘。<br />\n<br />\n香港人選擇嘅係尊嚴、自由、公義。靠依附極權而來嘅財富，其實只係出賣緊自己人格及後代利益嘅財富透支。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，請緊記，我哋無繼續低沉嘅本錢！寧化飛灰，不作微塵！"},{"pid":"3096bed71ac9a95427400a21f612bffedff8f088","tid":1995152,"uid":147419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T04:59:04.000Z","msg":"推佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771a5ed8865bb513487abb885acf58a233af2da4","tid":1995152,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31e169ae797f269976d31bfb71d374ba42605a36","tid":1995152,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T04:59:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a1632f527751497d151c8c460e626e765372703","tid":1995152,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16c7532050f01df5707955c47c15144d1191ab26","tid":1995152,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:00:02.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"ac5e8ca944644b1e261d8e01b3220829b138cad2","tid":1995152,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:00:14.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"47589bec881bbe1635207fb5cac10b0c225292f5","tid":1995152,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:00:24.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"a0703e69d8bbd99cba87d5249c90c66586521759","tid":1995152,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9da97bf2b2c8b7cc3b1232ef98028336272356","tid":1995152,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:00:38.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"e5ef6efabc189ed1e0